#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/mailer.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"It's time to configure the mailer to not simulate the sending of the emails.\n"
"The Quarkus mailer is using SMTP, so make sure you have access to an SMTP server."
